    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/ee8dca2fea1218cc7c7098e8e670442b.poster.avif?t=1745092982\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/ee8dca2fea1218cc7c7098e8e670442b.webm?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/ee8dca2fea1218cc7c7098e8e670442b.mp4?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Echoes of Exile</strong> is a short horror game about exploring space caves. You fly to points of interest and delve into the caves with your drone and flashlight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Send your drone out for recon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One of the few tools you have is a drone which can fit into places inaccessible to humans. It is a useful tool but not without it's limitations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/264c8fc230e1577a09f292c5bea2a385.poster.avif?t=1745092982\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/264c8fc230e1577a09f292c5bea2a385.webm?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/264c8fc230e1577a09f292c5bea2a385.mp4?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unravel the truth about what happened in these caves</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/70e7557872b4d2a5e98170f1669866a1.poster.avif?t=1745092982\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/70e7557872b4d2a5e98170f1669866a1.webm?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/70e7557872b4d2a5e98170f1669866a1.mp4?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A short horror experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/18454de2c9ca513a33282958d3119e74.poster.avif?t=1745092982\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/18454de2c9ca513a33282958d3119e74.webm?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/18454de2c9ca513a33282958d3119e74.mp4?t=1745092982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/3f60ea8b0d8b9be77d4db5414bb9a650.avif?t=1745092982\" width=800 height=117 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WISHLIST NOW</strong> to be notified of updates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
